  * Add a watchfile.
  * New upstream development version.
    - Pulled from http://josefsson.org/daily/gnutls/gnutls-20060930.tar.gz
    - Using a cvs snapshot instead of 1.5.1 because the soname in 1.5.1 was
      broken.
